Commander.

26
00:02:06,186 --> 00:02:07,027
Crisis at the border.

27
00:02:07,587 --> 00:02:08,466
Wutuo attacks Mingshui

28
00:02:08,626 --> 00:02:09,867
and Huayuan simultaneously.

29
00:02:11,947 --> 00:02:13,547
No time to waste. Go to the palace now.

30
00:02:18,051 --> 00:02:19,867
