31
00:02:19,867 --> 00:02:21,987
Wutuo actually broke the peace treaty

32
00:02:22,066 --> 00:02:23,267
and invaded us again.

33
00:02:24,066 --> 00:02:25,267
That's so unscrupulous!

34
00:02:26,147 --> 00:02:26,987
Xiao Jue.

35
00:02:27,107 --> 00:02:28,587
