39
00:02:35,746 --> 00:02:36,586
He Yan.

40
00:02:36,827 --> 00:02:38,226
I order you to lead the Fuyue Army

41
00:02:38,786 --> 00:02:40,307
and defend Rundu with Li Kuang

42
00:02:40,786 --> 00:02:42,107
to guard against Wutuo's raids.

43
00:02:43,226 --> 00:02:44,066
Your Majesty.

44
00:02:44,147 --> 00:02:45,226
There's no battle in Rundu.

45
00:02:45,746 --> 00:02:46,626
Yet Wutuo's forces

46
00:02:47,027 --> 00:02:48,066
are approaching Huayuan.

47
00:02:48,267 --> 00:02:49,107
It's threatening.

48
00:02:51,226 --> 00:02:52,387
There's no current conflict,

49
00:02:52,867 --> 00:02:54,906
but Wutuo is full of tricks.

50
00:02:55,547 --> 00:02:56,387
We must be alert.

51
00:02:57,027 --> 00:02:57,867
As for Huayuan,

52
00:02:58,506 --> 00:02:59,587
I've sent Yan He there,

53
00:03:00,267 --> 00:03:02,547
with Chu Zhao as military supervisor

54
00:03:02,946 --> 00:03:03,786
to assist.

55
00:03:10,867 --> 00:03:13,307
Yes, understood.

56
00:03:28,666 --> 00:03:30,186
His Majesty wants me to guard Rundu,

57
00:03:30,427 --> 00:03:31,466
but Li Kuang is there.

58
00:03:31,666 --> 00:03:32,666
Why send me too?

59
00:03:33,267 --> 00:03:34,107
In my opinion,

60
00:03:34,466 --> 00:03:35,867
His Majesty still distrusts us.

61
00:03:36,066 --> 00:03:38,227
An emperor's balance of power
is an age-old strategy.

62
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:39,867
But there's wisdom

63
00:03:40,226 --> 00:03:41,427
in this arrangement.

64
00:03:42,226 --> 00:03:44,427
Rundu lies between Huayuan and Mingshui.

65
00:03:44,746 --> 00:03:47,547
It allows quick support to both cities.

66
00:03:48,387 --> 00:03:49,227
Promise me

67
00:03:49,547 --> 00:03:50,906
you'll return safely.

68
00:03:53,307 --> 00:03:54,746
Take Wang Ba's team

69
00:03:55,147 --> 00:03:56,427
to Rundu with you.

70
00:03:57,066 --> 00:03:58,147
There's no battle there.

71
00:03:58,587 --> 00:03:59,746
Keep them with you.

72
00:04:00,107 --> 00:04:01,626
I have Feinu and Shen Han.

73
00:04:02,147 --> 00:04:03,066
With them guarding you,

74
00:04:03,387 --> 00:04:04,227
I'll feel assured.

75
00:04:05,786 --> 00:04:06,626
Okay.

76
00:04:12,346 --> 00:04:13,186
Miss He.

77
00:04:19,946 --> 00:04:21,747
Congratulations.
You've won imperial favor

78
00:04:22,426 --> 00:04:24,306
and secured the supervisor position.

79
00:04:54,346 --> 00:04:56,426
