83
00:05:07,027 --> 00:05:07,867
The baby kicked me.

84
00:05:10,866 --> 00:05:11,906
Behave yourself,

85
00:05:12,546 --> 00:05:14,787
or I'll punish you when I return.

86
00:05:15,027 --> 00:05:16,426
Don't threaten our baby.

87
00:05:24,187 --> 00:05:25,027
Yan He.

88
00:05:26,147 --> 00:05:26,987
This time,

89
00:05:27,747 --> 00:05:29,187
let me go with you.

90
00:05:30,306 --> 00:05:33,067
I went along with troops before.

91
00:05:34,666 --> 00:05:35,627
This is different!

92
00:05:36,027 --> 00:05:37,546
You're pregnant now.

93
00:05:38,707 --> 00:05:40,466
The due date is still weeks away.

94
00:05:41,866 --> 00:05:42,706
Besides,

95
00:05:43,387 --> 00:05:44,507
as a general's wife,

96
00:05:45,106 --> 00:05:46,907
I can endure hardships.

97
00:05:49,267 --> 00:05:50,107
Fine.

98
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:52,387
I'll stay by your side

99
00:05:52,666 --> 00:05:53,866
and see the birth of our baby.

100
00:05:59,147 --> 00:06:01,666
I'll be the best father in the capital.

101
