focus on the war.

105
00:06:28,587 --> 00:06:30,426
My wife and I will handle home affairs.

106
00:06:39,106 --> 00:06:39,946
Miss He.

107
00:06:39,986 --> 00:06:41,106
May you return safely.

108
00:07:09,123 --> 00:07:13,008
(Xiao Mansion)

109
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:28,400
(Rundu City)

110
00:07:57,026 --> 00:07:58,706
General He, time to eat.

111
00:08:19,147 --> 00:08:19,987
General He.

112
00:08:20,466 --> 00:08:22,507
I heard you returned
to write battle reports.

113
00:08:23,226 --> 00:08:24,147
Haven't started yet?

114
00:08:26,226 --> 00:08:27,106
Nothing to report.

115
00:08:27,707 --> 00:08:28,827
Wutuo forces

116
00:08:29,027 --> 00:08:30,387
continue assaults on Huayuan

117
00:08:30,747 --> 00:08:31,587
and Mingshui,

118
00:08:31,986 --> 00:08:33,466
while Rundu remains peaceful.

119
00:08:35,226 --> 00:08:36,066
General.

120
00:08:39,906 --> 00:08:40,946
General! Emergency!

121
00:08:41,906 --> 00:08:42,786
New battle report.

122
00:08:42,946 --> 00:08:44,186
Wutuo sent reinforcements

123
00:08:44,267 --> 00:08:45,107
to attack Huayuan.

124
00:08:46,267 --> 00:08:48,467
General Yan has fought nonstop
for two days.

125
00:08:50,787 --> 00:08:52,027
- Mai.
- Yes.

126
00:08:52,027 --> 00:08:52,987
You go tell Li Kuang

127
00:08:53,186 --> 00:08:54,387
that I'll leave 5,000 soldiers

128
00:08:54,507 --> 00:08:55,387
to defend the city.

129
00:08:56,946 --> 00:09:00,066
The rest will reinforce Huayuan with me.

130
00:09:00,747 --> 00:09:01,587
- Yes.
- Yes.

131
00:09:06,563 --> 00:09:09,679
(He)

132
00:09:28,227 --> 00:09:29,867
I heard you all rushed here

133
00:09:29,987 --> 00:09:30,867
