137
00:09:37,227 --> 00:09:40,627
- Great.
- Great.

138
00:09:40,946 --> 00:09:45,186
- Great.
- Great.

139
00:09:55,906 --> 00:09:58,146
Xiu, I'm back.

140
00:10:02,186 --> 00:10:03,107
He has returned.

141
00:10:31,027 --> 00:10:31,867
Madam.

142
00:10:32,066 --> 00:10:32,906
What's wrong?

143
00:10:40,467 --> 00:10:41,307
Careful, Madam.

144
00:10:42,306 --> 00:10:43,146
What's happening?

145
00:10:44,906 --> 00:10:45,746
Someone!

146
00:10:45,867 --> 00:10:46,946
Madam is going into labor.

147
00:10:47,107 --> 00:10:48,107
Someone!

148
00:10:50,467 --> 00:10:51,387
- General Yan!
- General!

149
00:10:51,467 --> 00:10:52,426
- General!
- General Yan!

150
00:10:53,546 --> 00:10:54,386
Medic!

151
00:10:54,507 --> 00:10:55,347
Medic!

152
00:10:55,507 --> 00:10:56,347
Medic!

153
00:10:56,706 --> 00:10:57,546
Don't.

154
00:10:59,347 --> 00:11:00,546
Don't tell Xiu.

155
00:11:02,066 --> 00:11:03,546
She's pregnant.

156
00:11:04,387 --> 00:11:05,306
Don't alarm her.

157
00:11:06,706 --> 00:11:07,627
Hang in there!

158
00:11:08,107 --> 00:11:09,107
The medic is coming.

159
00:11:10,467 --> 00:11:11,467
Promise me.

160
00:11:18,267 --> 00:11:19,107
Xiu.

161
00:11:21,946 --> 00:11:22,786
I'm sorry.

162
00:11:58,706 --> 00:11:59,906
Take a deep breath and push!

163
00:11:59,906 --> 00:12:01,027
Deep breath, Madam.

164
00:12:01,066 --> 00:12:01,906
Keep pushing!

165
00:12:01,906 --> 00:12:02,746
Push harder!

166
00:12:03,746 --> 00:12:05,186
Push! Keep pushing!

167
00:12:05,186 --> 00:12:06,026
Breathe in.

168
00:12:06,586 --> 00:12:07,426
Breathe in.

169
00:12:07,627 --> 00:12:08,467
Breathe in.

170
00:12:09,746 --> 00:12:10,586
Madam.

171
00:12:10,586 --> 00:12:11,786
Y-Yan He...

172
00:12:13,107 --> 00:12:14,027
Push, Madam!

173
00:12:14,267 --> 00:12:15,227
Push! Hold your breath!

174
00:12:16,946 --> 00:12:18,147
Hold it! Keep holding!

175
00:12:18,267 --> 00:12:19,107
Hold your breath!

176
00:12:19,107 --> 00:12:19,947
Almost done!

177
00:12:20,186 --> 00:12:21,026
Yan He

178
00:12:22,467 --> 00:12:25,027
is still mopping up remaining enemies
behind the lines.

179
00:12:25,267 --> 00:12:26,627
He'll return later.

180
00:12:26,627 --> 00:12:27,467
Push harder, Madam!

181
00:12:28,066 --> 00:12:29,706
Hold your breath and push!

182
00:12:29,706 --> 00:12:30,546
That's it!

183
00:12:30,546 --> 00:12:31,786
Hold and push!

184
00:12:34,267 --> 00:12:35,107
It's born!

185
00:12:38,107 --> 00:12:38,947
Madam!

186
00:12:39,347 --> 00:12:40,227
Congratulations!

187
00:12:40,627 --> 00:12:41,507
It's a girl!

188
00:12:41,546 --> 00:12:42,386
She's born, Madam!

189
00:12:42,666 --> 00:12:44,027
She's beautiful!

190
00:12:44,387 --> 00:12:45,227
Careful.

191
00:12:53,507 --> 00:12:54,586
It's Muxia.

192
00:12:55,586 --> 00:12:56,426
Muxia?

193
00:12:58,627 --> 00:12:59,546
Yan He chose this name.

194
00:13:00,306 --> 00:13:01,507
Liangjiang for a boy,

195
00:13:02,507 --> 00:13:03,867
Muxia for a girl.

196
00:13:06,426 --> 00:13:07,266
Muxia,

197
00:13:08,147 --> 00:13:09,666
your father is a great hero.

198
00:13:10,347 --> 00:13:11,627
Muxia, you will grow up

199
00:13:11,866 --> 00:13:13,906
to carry on your father's legacy.

200
00:13:16,107 --> 00:13:16,947
Muxia

201
00:13:18,186 --> 00:13:19,666
will become

202
00:13:20,546 --> 00:13:21,906
a good general

203
00:13:22,107 --> 00:13:22,947
like her father.

204
00:13:29,426 --> 00:13:30,266
So adorable.

205
00:13:33,467 --> 00:13:34,347
Muxia.

206
00:13:35,347 --> 00:13:36,187
Muxia.

207
00:13:40,676 --> 00:13:43,116
(Yan)

208
00:14:18,706 --> 00:14:21,666
Are Mrs. Yan and the child safe?

209
00:14:22,586 --> 00:14:23,426
Safe?

210
00:14:23,867 --> 00:14:24,707
Yes,

211
00:14:25,267 --> 00:14:26,107
they're safe.

212
00:14:26,627 --> 00:14:29,227
But the child lost her father at birth.

213
00:14:29,946 --> 00:14:30,867
Father and daughter

214
00:14:31,946 --> 00:14:34,267
never even met.

215
00:14:34,987 --> 00:14:37,867
This battle could have ended sooner

216
00:14:39,027 --> 00:14:40,306
with fewer casualties.

217
00:14:41,346 --> 00:14:43,747
All because of your loyal advice,

218
00:14:44,987 --> 00:14:45,946
His Majesty

219
00:14:47,027 --> 00:14:49,306
feared our concentrated military power,

220
00:14:50,107 --> 00:14:50,947
ordering me

221
00:14:51,627 --> 00:14:53,426
to station the Fuyue Army in Rundu,

222
00:14:54,826 --> 00:14:56,227
scattering our forces.

223
00:14:57,107 --> 00:14:59,306
So, we couldn't deliver
a decisive blow to Wutuo.

224
00:15:04,147 --> 00:15:05,267
Is this the outcome

225
00:15:06,946 --> 00:15:08,147
you wanted,

226
00:15:08,867 --> 00:15:09,906
Mr. Chu?

227
00:15:21,747 --> 00:15:23,027
You don't deserve to get wasted.

228
00:15:25,147 --> 00:15:27,066
Stay sober and atone for this.

229
00:15:35,306 --> 00:15:36,146
This is

230
00:15:36,627 --> 00:15:37,786
to honor the fallen soldiers.

231
00:15:49,267 --> 00:15:50,666
(Zilan, you're smart and diligent.)

232
00:15:50,826 --> 00:15:52,267
You will earn scholarly honors.

233
00:15:54,507 --> 00:15:55,467
When you grow up,

234
00:15:55,867 --> 00:15:57,867
you'll become a good
and respectable official.

235
00:15:58,706 --> 00:16:01,066
(Then no one will
dare bully you anymore.)

236
00:16:06,786 --> 00:16:07,626
Mother.

237
00:16:07,747 --> 00:16:09,027
Don't cry, Zilan.

238
00:16:09,586 --> 00:16:10,867
I'm just tired.

239
00:16:12,267 --> 00:16:14,347
My poor son.

240
00:16:15,467 --> 00:16:18,666
(Mother, I'll take you away
from the Chu family.)

241
00:16:19,467 --> 00:16:22,027
We don't have to endure their insult.

242
00:16:25,627 --> 00:16:26,467
Mother.

243
00:16:26,946 --> 00:16:28,186
Mother!

244
00:16:28,507 --> 00:16:30,627
(I only fear)

245
00:16:31,867 --> 00:16:33,786
you'll end up alone.

246
00:16:36,347 --> 00:16:37,426
From now on,

247
00:16:38,426 --> 00:16:39,627
stop pushing yourself so hard.

248
00:16:41,507 --> 00:16:43,227
Spare yourself.

249
00:16:45,508 --> 00:16:48,241
♪Upon towering fortress walls♪

250
00:16:48,485 --> 00:16:51,089
♪Brooding over lamented pasts♪

251
00:16:51,268 --> 00:16:54,129
♪Where shall light be found♪

252
00:16:54,129 --> 00:16:56,080
♪Once♪

253
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:59,152
♪I had an unbreakable faith♪

254
00:17:00,836 --> 00:17:01,923
You know what?

255
00:17:03,387 --> 00:17:04,227
You are

256
00:17:06,186 --> 00:17:08,186
becoming like Xu Jingfu.

257
00:17:08,186 --> 00:17:10,906
♪Resent old dreams like drifting clouds♪

258
00:17:11,187 --> 00:17:13,005
♪Heartache♪

259
00:17:13,005 --> 00:17:15,979
♪Resenting the lonely years♪

260
00:17:16,826 --> 00:17:17,666
I believed

261
00:17:19,066 --> 00:17:20,707
I upheld moral principles,

262
00:17:22,066 --> 00:17:23,586
unlike scum like Xu Jingfu.

263
00:17:25,467 --> 00:17:26,307
Now,

264
00:17:27,427 --> 00:17:28,987
stubbornness blinded me.

265
00:17:29,866 --> 00:17:30,907
Endless warfare,

266
00:17:31,786 --> 00:17:32,947
widespread suffering,

267
00:17:34,027 --> 00:17:35,267
families torn apart,

268
00:17:35,907 --> 00:17:37,227
all because of me.

269
00:17:39,427 --> 00:17:40,267
If the ruler

270
00:17:43,146 --> 00:17:44,907
and ministers had been united,

271
00:17:45,707 --> 00:17:46,907
with generals defending Wei,

272
00:17:48,187 --> 00:17:49,667
Wutuo would've never invaded!

273
00:17:57,947 --> 00:17:58,907
I was wrong.

274
00:18:15,987 --> 00:18:16,827
General He.

275
00:18:17,147 --> 00:18:17,987
Urgent news!

276
00:18:17,987 --> 00:18:18,907
It's Mingshui.

277
00:18:19,187 --> 00:18:20,386
After losing in Huayuan,

278
00:18:20,546 --> 00:18:21,947
Wutuo sent more troops to Mingshui.

279
00:18:22,306 --> 00:18:23,467
Their troops from Huayuan

280
00:18:23,707 --> 00:18:24,947
are already advancing there.

281
00:18:25,947 --> 00:18:27,227
The Xiao Army can't

282
00:18:27,626 --> 00:18:29,267
resist much longer with weak forces.

283
00:18:30,346 --> 00:18:31,467
We must reinforce them!

284
00:18:32,106 --> 00:18:33,906
Mr. Jiang, you stay here.

285
00:18:34,146 --> 00:18:36,426
Assist General Yan's deputy
in defending Huayuan.

286
00:18:36,907 --> 00:18:37,747
Understood!

287
00:18:55,546 --> 00:18:56,386
Xiao Jue!

288
00:18:56,747 --> 00:18:58,146
Surrender now,

289
00:18:58,586 --> 00:19:00,546
